<br>
Things they could do with a 5 level increase and not screw up balance.<br>
1) hp/mana increase.<br>
2) new spells(i dont mean upgrades to current spells i mean new spells designed specifially for planes of power that dont work in the old world)<br>
3) ofcourse the higher level working for you in all combt calculations(wich is a huge benefit in and of itself)<br>
4) lower discipline resuse timers(but there would have to be a lower cap, this working with defensive would make the skill even more broken and overpowered then it already is)<br>
5) having level 65 open up a new AA skill tree. But that skill tree would most likely have major prereqs for all the skills in it, which it should. PoP should also add AA skills in the other trees as well tho; i can think of a lot of nice arch skills that wouldnt mess anything up.<br>
<br>
